HE WAS beaten and stripped naked for allegedly robbing someone at an ATM. A video of an alleged card scammer being beaten up has surfaced on social media. The video was shared by Man’s Not Barry Roux on Twitter. In the video, a group of people are seen beating up a naked man accused of card skimming. It is not yet clear where and and when the incident occurred. The man could be seen being dragged and beaten repeatedly by people who keep on saying: "beat this dog, beat this dog..where is the card...where is the card...he must be beaten so that he may not do it again”. 